---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="My Curriculum">
	<main>
        <div class="presentation">

            <div class=text_presentation>
                <h1>Sergio Andres Ramirez</h1>      
                
            </div>
            <div class="img__presentation">
                <img src="Photo__Perfil.jpeg" alt="foto__perfil">
            </div>
            
            <h2>Web Developer</h2>
            <p>I am a front-end web developer with solid knowledge of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, as well as practical experience in frameworks such as Angular, React, and Astro. My focus is on creating engaging and functional user experiences. I also have basic skills in Java, C++, and familiarity with the Linux console. Passionate about creating intuitive and optimized interfaces, I am looking for opportunities that challenge me to continue growing in the world of web development.</p>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    body {
        font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
        
    }

    .presentation {
        font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
        width: 80%;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
    }

    .text_presentation {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .text_presentation h1 {
        margin-right: 20px;
        color: #204683;
    }

    .img__presentation {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .img__presentation img {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        border-radius: 50%;
    }

    h2 {
        color: #204683;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }

    p{
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 1.3em; 
    }

</style>